originalText.text: Our building has utilized Dynasty Property management services for the better part of 3 years. During those three years, we have found Bob and his team to be immensly helpful, responsive, thoughtful, value-oriented and reputable. I would recommend Dynasty to other buildings looking for management assistance.

originalText.text: Dynasty Property management is awful and deserves zero stars. Robert Friedman and Richard DeNardo have failed to take action and respond to any requests or emails in over a year. The positive reviews here are likely created by the owner or company. Speak to the owners and renters in these properties and they will all share the same exact story; management ignores emails, never addresses concerns, have made empty promises in the past; however, they profit off working class residents and collect a monthly fee for doing nothing. Stay away.
